{"_path":"/city/t013","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"桃園好孕專車2024/03/08上路","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t013.jpeg","sequence":13,"category":"社會福利","author":"婦幼局","link":"https://www.facebook.com/sun0976315743/posts/pfbid02pbaJBCuzrH3eYeBh3cerZLdSWwU3rxSEtAYnwsrgpHSkf8GQZoX7aKHSa34aPe7l","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-06T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"桃園好孕專車-20240308-上路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園好孕專車 2024/03/08 上路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://babycare.tycg.gov.tw/#/news-detail/4385a4de-3db5-4a07-8e0c-26be6f8e0e81"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園育兒資源網"}]},{"type":"text","value":":"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一、計畫說明"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n桃園市政府(以下簡稱本府)為保障孕婦交通安全與便利，規劃孕期至預產期日後七個月內搭乘合作計程車之車資補助，滿足產檢、生產、產後回診、嬰兒預防保健醫療、產後心理諮商等乘車需求，透過便利的交通措施，營造友善的生養環境，特訂定本計畫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二、補助說明"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（一）補助對象"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n設籍本市之孕產婦，或配偶設籍本市之非本國籍孕產婦。\n孕婦須為懷孕中，且已領有孕婦健康手冊；\n產婦為 113 年 1 月 1 日(含當日)後生產之產婦均可申請。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（二）補助內容"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n每趟次最高補助 250 元，總補助金額 9,000 元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"（三）使用效期"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n孕婦：自孕期起至預產期次日後七個月。\n產婦：113 年 1 月 1 日(含當日)後生產者，自分娩日之次日後七個月。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三、申辦方式"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n113 年 3 月 8 日起，至"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://babycare.tycg.gov.tw/#/news-detail/4385a4de-3db5-4a07-8e0c-26be6f8e0e81"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園育兒資源網"}]},{"type":"text","value":"進行線上申請，無須臨櫃申辦，省時又方便。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"四、申辦資料"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（一）為孕婦者，檢具孕婦健康手冊或診斷證明書； 為產婦者，檢具新生兒出生證明。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（二）申請人國民身分證正反面+戶口名簿或戶籍謄本。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（三）申請人為非本國籍孕（產）婦，具有效之居留證件及配偶之國民身分證正反面+戶口簿或戶籍謄本。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（四）六個月內二吋半身、正面脫帽數位相片帽數位相片。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"五、合作車隊"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n請向客服人員「指定搭乘桃園市好孕計程車」"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3010-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3010-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3010-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3010-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3010-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3010-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3010-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3010-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3010-5.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3010-5.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"桃園好孕專車-20240308-上路","depth":2,"text":"桃園好孕專車 2024/03/08 上路"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t013.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t013.md","_extension":"md"}